java.lang.Object
Compiler.AntlrGenerated.BuffBaseListener
Compiler.SymbolTable.SymbolTableGeneratorListener
All Implemented Interfaces:
BuffListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
public class SymbolTableGeneratorListener
extends BuffBaseListener
Listener responsible for making the symbol table. Provides scopes and globalScope for use by other listeners/visitors
